	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This has been driving me nuts for a long time.<br /><br />I remembered playing this game on a Game Boy Phat when I was prob 10. And one distinguishing characteristic I remembered all too well was Pauline's scream, which doesn't seem to be emulated on BGB, Goomba Color, any of the Youtube videos I see, &amp; I can't find it on the GBS file.<br /><br />I was starting to get convinced maybe I was just crazy, but then I played the rom on VisualBoy Advance &amp; it plays it just as I remembered! <img src="./images/smilies/icon_eek.gif" alt=":shock:" title="Shocked" /> <br /><br />Why is this one sound effect so elusive? Is it a PCM? And is there any way to get it to work on Goomba?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


